<h1 style='text-align:left'>About Bitcoin</h1>

<dl>
<dt>What is Bitcoin?
<dd><a target="_blank" href="http://bitcoin.org/">Bitcoin</a> is a revolutionary <i>digital currency</i>.

<dt>Who uses Bitcoin?
<dd>Anyone can use Bitcoin by running software on your computer.

<dt>Why use Bitcoin?
<dd>Bitcoin provides no-overhead instant irreversible payment transactions.
</dl>

<br /><hr /><br />

<h1>Island Forge + Bitcoin</h1>

<p>We're excited to accept Bitcoin and think it's the most remarkable technology since the Internet itself.</p>

<p style='text-align:center;font-size:large'><a href='/membership/'>Upgrade your account with Bitcoin!</a></p>

